metadata.name: Undersea world
metadata.description:
By Kris Sova

What if there are mermaids in the underwater world? What do you think they can do there? What do they like, where do they work? I suggest you take a break from the problems of the modern world and plunge into fantasy! Be simple, easy as children. After all, children are always happy and without limits. Let's try?
